×031Between   the   Lines×
×031=====================×
Arriving to the trainstation 'Bingen (am Rhein)', and
lucky me I don't live more than 3 hours away from the
Breakpoint  city. With a take-away coffee in the hand
I  wait  for the party shuttle-bus service to appear.
Breakpoint bus service is a very nice service for the
attenders  and while dipping my fingers in the coffee
mug,  my  third  brain  (the  demobrain)  wake up and
suddenly  I'm  in deep thoughts of this years events,
for  example  who will release what in the Amiga demo
compo.

Suspecting  that  ×031Ephidrena×  wanted to ruin the plans
for  a  The  Black Lotus 5-times a row domination.. I
simply  asked  ×031Loaderror× some weeks before the party.
And  he  never  hesitate  for   an   honest   answer:
×008  Damn those arrogant Swedes.. I've got a cold,×
×008  so coding  the  demo  is  kind   of   painful..×
As  a  consequence,  I understood that the norwegians
wouldn't  submit  anything here. Instead I could just
hope  that the ×031Loonies× team (Psycho-Blueberry-Farfar)
would  take over the sparkling torch for a fair fight
against   ×031the   Black   Lotus×   demo   making.

-Where  do  you  want  to  go  with the BP bus? While
waiting,  the shuttle bus has quittly arrived and the
driver  asks me with a grin. A good answer would have
been:  
-is  there  life  on mars? then bring me there today,
but please, do not take too long time,   since I have
a deadline in a competition...   Instead, I answered:
-to , eerhm [cough, cough] Breakpoint.     Five pico-
secounds  later,  I  realize  the lameness in my 
question. ×00820 persons, without cosmotautic outfits× are
sharing this four-wheel rocket waiting for me to take
seat to  the  Breakpoint   journey.

