×031Amiga   Demo×
×031============×
Before  the  Amiga  demo  was  about  to  start   the
atmosphere  was  quite weired (in a positive way) and
when  starting  with  the total lame demo by ×031Hardcore×
×031Lamers×,  the audience already here starts to applause
honestly. For me the right mood arrived together with
×031Drifters×  cartoon-like  demo  shown  as  entry  no 2.
Typically for the french group are three elements: 1)
Pure animations (the palm too?) and 2) very cute, and
3)   syncronised   and   great!
Two  finnish  guys  from the group ×031Function×, made the
demo  'Step  by  Step'  with  help  of  one  borrowed
computer  from  ×031Tulou×.  So the sample in use could be
