morning.  Then ×031Loonies× delivered a nice Demo (the 5th
entry  shown). Especially I liked those Aeroplanes in
the  end,  or  the credit part with blurred graphics.
This  kind  of  switching  between focus and smoothed
graphics  reminds me from ×031Wrath Designs× demo 'Gyrate'
from  Assembly 1996 (just a tiny difference that this
was 3d modelling, and WD made it in 2d). The audience
yields   'Looooonies'.   After   the   danish   demo
production, the compo machine has to reboot before it
was  time for ×031Mad Wizards× entry 'Glare'. This was the
only  PPC  demo.  The  audience   yields   'Maaaaawi,
Maaaaawi'.
